Providing for consideration of the Senate amendment to the bill (H.R. 5371) making continuing appropriations and extensions for fiscal year 2026, and for other purposes.

action.text: The House Committee on Rules reported an original measure, H. Rept. 119-372, by Mrs. Fischbach.
The resolution makes in order a motion that the House concur in the Senate amendment to H.R. 5371 and provides for one hour of debate.

calendar.text: Placed on the House Calendar, Calendar No. 46.

action.text: DEBATE - The House proceeded with one hour of debate on H. Res. 873.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to by recorded vote: 213 - 209 (Roll no. 284).

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: This resolution provides for House consideration of Senate Amendment 3937 to H.R. 5371, Continuing Appropriations, Agriculture, Legislative Branch, Military Construction and Veterans Affairs, and Extensions Act, 2026.
